Dataset
-------

The dataset (the data/ directory and viz/empire_evolution.html, together with
the graph embedded in it) is released into the public domain under the
Creative Commons CC0 1.0 Universal Public Domain Dedication:
https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/legalcode

You may copy, modify, distribute, and use the data, including for commercial
purposes, without asking permission. Attribution is appreciated but not
required: a citation to the paper helps others find the source and is
welcome, but you are under no obligation to provide one.

The dataset incorporates Wikidata identifiers (QIDs), which are themselves
CC0. The curated assembly, date research, typology decisions, and
relationship structure contributed by this work are likewise dedicated to
the public domain under CC0.


